Payment can be in any local currency, through a variety of methods (e.g. ACH, Global ACH, wire, pre-paid debit card, live check, cash, etc.). All tax and regulatory (OFAC/AML fraud protection) is streamlined by Tipalti.

_source.name: Fivetran
_source.html:
Fivetran replicates applications, databases, events and files into a high-performance data warehouse, after a five minute setup. The vendor says their standardized cloud pipelines are fully managed and zero-maintenance.

The vendor says Fivetran began with a realization: For modern companies using cloud-based software and storage, traditional ETL tools badly underperformed, and the complicated configurations they required often led to project failures. To streamline and accelerate analytics projects, Fivetran developed zero-configuration, zero-maintenance pipelines to deliver data into modern cloud warehouses. 

Shaped by the real-world needs of data analysts and business intelligence users, Fivetran technology promises to enable organizations to control their data without complex engineering and ultimately supports data-backed decisions and company culture.

_source.html:

DIS docks with a variety of third-party data collection tools and provides an Agent/SDK. _source.name: Improvado
_source.description:
Improvado, headquartered in San Francisco, aims to help marketers & agencies drive ROI by consolidating all their data so they can make informed decisions about their marketing campaigns. 
Integrations include: Google, Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, Linkedin, Pinterest, Twitter, Adwords, Outbrain, Taboola, and Adroll. The solution is designed to to take the pain out of data-driven marketing by aggregating, transforming and visualizing cross-channel marketing data.
screenshots: An extensive list of data sources to pull the data
Connections
The DataPrep tool to transform the data efficiently
_source.html:
Improvado is an ETL platform that extracts data from various data sources, transforms normalized data, and loads the results to a final destination, with over 200 integrations. Improvado pulls sales and marketing data at many granular dimensions, such as campaign level, geo level, ad level, keyword level, etc. With this approach, the vendor states marketers can identify actionable insights based on their dataset.

First, data is collected from different platforms and normalized by the Improvado ONE module. Improvado's universal REST API consolidates data from connected data sources into ONE. The service works at a low level, behaving like a proxy.
This means the user needs only one API instead of dozens to:
Connect data sources via OAuth (login/password etc.)Discover available accounts, campaigns, metrics, etc.Place data extraction tasks and get resultsONE module simplifies scaling, error unification and reduces upkeep.
The vendor states Improvado's data preparation and Marketing Common Data Model accelerate the speed at which data is made available to businesses and save on the costly engineering resources that are traditionally required for complex data transformations.
Because marketing teams and data analysts spend too much time cleaning data instead of analyzing it, Improvado's data preparation capabilities are designed to provide a self-service, point-and-click tool to quickly identify errors and apply rules that can reuse and share, even across massive data sets.

With Improvado marketing common data model (MCDM), an add-on,  users can standardize marketing data, regardless of source, to make it equally useful across the enterprise. Improvado MCDM works as a pre-configured template for an automated cross-channel normalization across various data sources. This is to support common marketing analytics use-cases, such as cross-channel analytics, multi-channel attribution, etc.

_source.name: ZenRows
_source.html:
Web Scraping API & Proxy Server
ZenRows API handles rotating proxies, headless browsers, and CAPTCHAs. It can collect content from any website with an API call, and offers a Proxy connection.
ZenRows will bypass any anti-bot or blocking system to help obtain the info desired. For that, it includes several options such as Javascript Rendering or Premium Proxies. There is also the autoparse option that will return structured data automatically. It will convert unstructured content into structured data (JSON output), with no code necessary.
ZenRows boasts a high accuracy and success rate without any human intervention. No more CAPTCHAs or setting up proxies. Some domains are especially complicated (i.e., Instagram), and for those, Premium Proxies are usually required. After enabling them, the success rate will be higher. In case the request returns an error, ZenRows will not compute nor charge that request. Only successful requests will count.
API and Proxy modes are available; choose the one that best suits the task. ZenRows also released a Node SDK, but it can be integrated into any codebase. There are examples in the website for different technologies and languages: cURL, Python, Node, Go, PHP, Ruby, and Java.
It also handles the required infrastructure for scraping at scale. ZenRows handles all the proxy connections, headless browsers, rendering, servers, and so on. And with an Unlimited Scale, scrape the web with unlimited bandwidth.

Defining where the data is pushed to and from and who has access rights is also taken care of within the platform; whether its Azure, Hanah, Google Drive, Amazon S3, Twitter, Google Sheets, visual tools or another environment.The IntelligenceSurrounding the core engine, Dexi has built-in intelligence layers that extend its data capture capability, increases its level of automation and breadth of application. Advanced mapping through our Product Manager feature that minimises effort and maximises automation to categorise data and enable robots to â€˜learnâ€™ each time new or unexpected data is encountered; and overcoming barriers and techniques employed by some web sites, such as the ability to automatically solve Captchas.Also, through collaboration with customers a whole host of other features enhance the intelligence of the overall solution, including; Product Compliance, Smart Data Feeds, â€˜Buy nowâ€™ product options â€“ that connects every retailer to your brand, competitor intelligence, pricing alerts and AI.The ResultToday, Dexi offers a Commerce Intelligence solution armed with features and services that allow businesses to capture, structure and ingest up-to-the-minute web data and extend its use to augment databases, provide immediate business insights or use directly in â€˜smart feedsâ€™ for digital marketplace commerce.

_source.name: Onit ExtractAI
_source.html: Artificial Intelligence to Handle the Post-Signature PhaseOnitâ€™s ExtractAI software uses artificial intelligence (AI) to extract and obtain usable data from executed, legacy, and third-party paper contracts. In the post-signature phase, ExtractAI applies practical AI to data extraction projects and produces higher quality data than traditional tools. By adding an AI component to these data extraction projects, companies can cut costs, reduce risk and save time.Extracting Data with AIArtificial intelligence turns contract data into actionable information at scale.Batch Review: Extract data from multiple legal documents at once for due diligence, applying contract updates, or for importing legacy contracts.Repapering: Contract details and key terms can be amended or redlined due to regulatory, policy, or commercial changes or M&A activities.Contract Abstraction: Identify key legal, clauses, terms, and details in documents such as contract agreements for analysis and management.Audit Compliance: Automate large-scale legal contract review during regulatory changes and export relevant details to .CSV reports and in-document notes.Due Diligence: Automate the batch review of contracts for routine legal due diligence, making time for higher-value M&A tasks.Legacy Contract Migration: Legacy contracts metadata can be rapidly analyzed to extract critical dates, terms, and clauses to assist in the import.Contract Lifecycle Management Integration: Integrate ExtractAI into your Onit or third-party contract management system for AI-assisted workflows.

The platform comes equipped with the tools for reading documents, data extraction and classification, natural language processing, and optical character recognition. It is designed to enable creators, developers, and organizations to quickly build complex business applications based on their needs.

_source.html:
Mailparser is an email parsing and workflow automation app, from SureSwift Capital. Users can define custom parsing rules which will extract data fields from the email body, the subject, the sender or even from attached files (CSV, XLS, PDF, HTML). Parsed data fields are available in form of spreadsheets or can be transferred to other web applications with webhook integrations.

Mailparser FeaturesSend emails to mailparser.io and get structured data in return. Its web-based email processing software allows the user to pull any kind of data from recurring emails. Discover Mailparser features and transform unstructured text into data fields.

Custom email parsermailparser.io allows users to extract data from the email body, the subject, the sender information or even from attached files. They offer ready-to-use templates for the most common email parsing tasks. Also, users can create custom parsing rules, or chain up as many text filters as needed to crop, clean and refine data.

Pull data from file attachmentsParse data from email file attachments. You can pull text from various file formats (PDF, DOC, DOCX, XLS, CSV, TXT, XML, â€¦) then use filters to refine, crop and transform the data.


Move data to where it belongsExtracting data from emails is just the first step when it comes to automating business processes. Update an Excel file, Word document, a CRM or a database, send a reply email, save email attachments to cloud storage, â€¦ The possibilities for automating a business includes Salesforce actions and other systems.


Automate business processesOnce extracted data is available it can be sent to hundreds of web-apps in real-time. Users can also send the parsed data to their own scripts which creates the possibility of automating business processes. Downloading the data in Excel, CSV, JSON, or XML, are, according to the vendor, user favorites.


Value Proposition
mailparser.io was built to support a variety of use-cases and boasts a flexible architecture. The user can set up custom parsing rules step-by-step. mailparser.io runs directly in a browser without anything to install, and setting up parsing rules is set up to be easy, and require no technical skills.

_source.name: Docparser

_source.html:
Docparser is a cloud-based document data extraction and automation tool in the market today. Using OCR and ML technology, the solution aims to make manual data processing more streamlined.
Parse documentsExtract data from recurring documents - such as PDFs, Word docs and scanned image files. Users can parse invoices, shipping documents, bank statements, HR forms, and sales projections.
Send data, to where it's most usefulOnce that data is extracted, it can send data to 100's of endpoints. That could be a direct download to Excel, CSV, JSON or XML, or integrate directly with apps such as Google Sheets, Salesforce, custom webhooks or using 3rd party favourites such as Zapier, Integromat and MS Power Automate, connect to 100's of other endpoints.
Customize with RulesUsers can take advantage of standard rules, created to recognize the most common document fields - such as date, invoice number or values within a table for example. If you need a more powerful solution, build on existing rules, or start a document 'parser' from scratch with a suite of options.
Can be tried freeDocparser offers a free forever option, with an extended trial.

_source.html:
MMC Receipt app is a receipt scanning, processing and expense management app that helps scan receipts and provides instant pushing to accounting software for a receipt management experience. The MMC Receipt app is brought by the makers of MMC Convert and MMC Books.Combining machine learning and regular human checks, the app aims to provide fast, instant and hassle-free expense management every single time.The MMC Receipt app helps scan receipts and provides instant pushing to QuickBooks Online, QuickBooks Desktop, FreshBooks, Xero, to provide a complete receipt management experience. If the user does not have an associated accounting software, scanned receipts can be simply exported in an excel/CSV format.The app includes features like Unlimited users, Unlimited cloud storage and Unlimited Receipt Scanning and processing, in order to make it a convenient business receipt tracker and a handy receipt management tool.MMC Receipt app has a fixed, flat pricing of 15 USD a month for unlimited receipt processing. Unlike receipt scanning apps that increase their prices as the number of documents increase, MMC Receipt prices remain constant for unlimited receipts, unlimited users and unlimited cloud storage.The receipt capturing app also offers other features like multiple formats, multiple currency support, super-fast pushing to many accounting softwares and an always-available support team.It is free to try out for a month, with all the features and without entering credit card details.How MMC Receipt app worksUsers can capture and upload receipts using:* The camera on a mobile phone* Email* Scans on a computerAfter a receipt is uploaded, MMC Receipt will automatically read all of the key information and display it in a manageable format, for processing with linked accounting software or, if there is not accounting software, the ability to export into an excel format.The vendor's value proposition for MMC Receipt :1) Processing Time < 5-minute2) Capture receipts, see the data get updated in real-time.3) Data Precision4) Multi-Currency 5) Instant Pushing to Accounting Software6) Line Item Description7) Flexible Data Capture8) Export into Excel/CSV File format9) Customizable and ready to be integrated with any accounting software
MMC Receipt also has a reseller program to work closely with accountants and bookkeepers where resellers can earn up to 150 USD per subscription.

_source.name: ChronoScan
_source.description: ChronoScan capture is a suite for document and data capture applications. ChronoScan provides simple capture as well as complex high volume extraction and line item data capture. It also offers a server-client solution for big enterprises, or a free edition with limited features for single users.
_source.html:
ChronoScan is a software suite for document scanning & PDF/OCR data capture. It allows users to Scan/Index large sets of documents, helping with data entry with OCR & Assisted auto fields. Users can extract text from PDF Files and convert to indexed data, and upload documents to the cloud, or export documents & data to a CRM or ERP system.

While the ADV/PRO edition was created for smaller entities or single users, and there is also a free edition for single users, the ChronoScan Enterprise was created for big paper and data workloads with focus on a multi-user environment and scalability. Built on a server-client infrastructure ChronoScan Enterprise can be used to process a wider range of different documents and partially or fully automate a workflow.

ChronoScan Enterprise features include:
Client/Server Architecture - Centralise all the data processing and administration tasks while spreading the power to many simultaneous users.Thin Client Interface -  Daily tasks are performed through a lightweight client interface.Multiuser Support - Spread the same tasks amongst several users simultaneously to complete them faster.Multilingual GUI - Fast access to several different interface languages.User Role Support -  Create a user hierarchy to control access and separate different tasks.Automated Workflow - Automated input via hotfolders or IMAP and automated output will give users immediate access to documents and data.Multiple Servers - Extra machines can be added as servers to easily scale any installation.Server Load Balancing - With more than one server machine the throughoutput rate scales with the number of machines installed.Notifications Engine - The notifications engine can give system administrators even more control and will help all users to keep the workflow moving.IMAP Client - ChronoScan Enterprise comes bundled with a flexible IMAP automated input module taking out the need for any additional software.Logging and User Statistics - System administrators will have full access to every action performed on the system by every user on a easy to use Reports Engine.High Speed Browser Editing Users will have accesss to a simple user interface with all the tools needed to index documents.Cloud Scanning Client - Documents can be scanned from any client on the network without any need for manual transfer of files or extra software.Security -  Boasting a flexible and complete user role and access framework, it is designed so that it is easy to control what users have access to what features and documents.
